# Build artefacts
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/bin-checkbuild/
**/bin-checkbuild2/
**/out/
**/publish/

# IDE / Editor
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.swp

# Source control
**/.git/
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes
**/.github/

# Local secrets and dev-only configuration
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/secrets.json
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Runtime data we never want to bake into an image
**/logs/
**/*.log

# Misc / docs that bloat the image but aren't needed at runtime
**/*.md
**/Docs/
**/Properties/launchSettings.json

# Container metadata
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml

# Cross-project folders that may be present from monorepo checkouts
DMS-Frontend/
MigrationTools/
